<!-- Modal 1 - How It Works -->
<div class="modal fade" id="howItWorksModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">How to Use This Site</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>There are 2 ways to navigate this site when checking in:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Click/tap a marker on the map that corresponds to your current location.</li>
          <li>Select your current Camera from <em>The Cameras</em> dropdown in the top nav bar.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>Enter your name and comment in the form and hit submit. (Need some comment inspiration? Hit the <span style="color:red">(?)</span> .) Your check-in will be saved.</p>
        <p>Upload a photo from your phone or tablet by clicking the 'Choose photo' button, browse to the correct folder and click upload, or take a photo with your camera and click upload.</p>
        <p style="color:#c0392b"><b>If you're submitting a photo, ONLY TAP THE SUBMIT BUTTON ONCE. And be patient. Our uploader can take some time, especially if the photo's large.</b></p> 
        <br>
        <h3>Visiting after the hike is over?</h3>
        <p>There are 3 ways to navigate the comments on the site:</p>
        <ol>
          <li>Via the markers on the map.</li>
          <li>Via The Camera's dropdown in the top nav.</li>
          <li>Via "All the checkins" link just next to it. Filter your results by station!</li>
        </ol>
        <p>Thanks for visiting and/or participating in <em>On Camera: The Watchmen</em></p>
        <p>~ Peter and Chris</p>
        </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
